== 评价 ==
* 剧版《赵氏孤儿案》不单是讲述程婴救孤的故事，更着力于表现程婴与屠岸贾的暗中较量，是一次没有笑场的优质改编，观众认为“颇具电影范儿”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/ent/2013/03/22/254537.html|title=《赵氏孤儿案》 一次没有笑场的优质改编|accessdate=2017-09-27|author=|date=2013-03-22|last=|work=|publisher=新京报|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927112257/http://www.bjnews.com.cn/ent/2013/03/22/254537.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 本剧在央视播出后，尽管媒体和网络对该剧一边倒地叫好，但收视率始终处于不温不火的状态，对此导演阎建钢表示如今严肃又不炒话题的剧可谓“孤掌难鸣”，观众更愿意选择娱乐性强的电视剧<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/zz/detail_2013_04/03/23829930_0.shtml?_from_ralated|title=《赵氏孤儿案》收视不如口碑 正剧难敌雷剧|accessdate=2017-09-27|author=|date=2013-04-03|work=|publisher=凤凰网|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113108/http://ent.ifeng.com/zz/detail_2013_04/03/23829930_0.shtml?_from_ralated|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* 剧版《赵氏孤儿案》通过程婴亲手摔死儿子的巨大牺牲，实际上肯定并赞扬传统的忠义价值观。这引发观众争议，多是褒扬，但批判也有<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/m/2013-04-10/112126784419.shtml|title=央视大戏《赵氏孤儿案》收宫 价值观引争议|accessdate=2017-09-27|author=|date=2013-04-10|work=|publisher=新浪|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927112217/http://news.sina.com.cn/m/2013-04-10/112126784419.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ent.ifeng.com/idolnews/yuping/detail_2013_04/05/23891711_0.shtml|title=揭秘《赵氏孤儿案》火热背后：正剧饥渴症|accessdate=2017-09-27|author=|date=2013-04-05|work=|publisher=凤凰网|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113627/http://ent.ifeng.com/idolnews/yuping/detail_2013_04/05/23891711_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

